sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client as API Route or Agent
    participant Queue as Job Table / Redis State
    participant Worker as Job Consumer
    participant Store as Backend DB
    participant UI as Dashboard

    Client->>Queue: Enqueue job request
    Queue-->>Client: Job id and queued state
    Worker->>Queue: Claim pending job
    Worker->>Store: Load job payload and update status
    Worker->>Worker: Execute the requested workflow
    Worker->>Store: Persist completed result and timestamps
    Worker-->>UI: New job state visible through API polling
